                             ARCADE TIPS

Taken from various sources. Typed in by Parasite.


HARD DRIVIN'

Put the car into top speed, switch back into neutral. You are noe Šinvincible to all collisions and can travel constantly at top speed.


OPERATION THUNDERBOLT

Get a highscore, and type your name as WIGAN NINJA (including the Šspace). This gives you infinate continues to play, and you can skip to Šthe next level by pressing F7. Or enter your name as SPECCY MODE to Šmake it harder!!!


SWITCHBLADE

Get a highscore, and type your name as POOKY, THEN PRESSING 1,2,3,4,or Š5 on the title screen lets you jump between levels


NINJA WARRIORS

These are some strange backdoors....
To activate all these you must first press CAPS LOCK, type the Šsentence, and depress CAPS LOCK to activate them.
THE TERMINATOR  - Ninja body parts explode when you die.
MONTY PYTHON    - Enemies come on backwards.
SKIPPY		- Enemise bounce.
A SMALL STEP FOR MANKIND  - Baddies will jump off the screen.
STEVE AUSTIN    - Press S during play to activate slow motion.


INDIANNA JONES & THE LAST CRUSADE

Type JEHOVA on the title screen to activate the cheat mode. Now press ŠL to skip levels, and 1 and 2 to move around within that level.


GHOULS & GHOSTS

To become invincible from baddies, Press fire to start and type ŠSTEPHEN BROADHURST


CYBERNOID

Press <space> on the title screen and type RAISTLIN, now press <space> Šagain for infinate lives. To advance to the next level, pause the game Šand press N.